text.en_US: Now playing: Your Contract has Expired

message.en_US: Hi!
Oh hello Lea. I see you brought your Schneider friends along with you.
Ja! Here we are, in the digital flesh!
You wanted to see us?
Yes, it is good to see both of you!
I was actually wondering if you guys could help me with some research.
Us? I'm not exactly a scientific genius, you know. Are you sure it won't be too advanced?.
Oh I'm sure you are quite suited for the job.
You see, I am trying to further study the effects of evotar creation, however it is difficult due to my limited sample size.
Most evotars are unaware of the truth and won't react well to seeing their human-avatar counterpart.
I've worked with Lea and Shizuka, however Lea was created quite a while ago and has grown into her own personality by now.
You could say that again.
If she didn't share my face, you'd never even be able to make the connection.
Luke, because you have accepted the truth about yourself and have retained all your memories, you can greatly help me with evotar research.
So what do you need me to do? Are you going to run tests on us?
I suppose you could call it that. But I think you'll be happy to participate.
I would like you and Lukas to \c[3]duel\c[0] while I collect some data.
Duel? Wouldn't that be like fighting against myself?
Fighting against my own self... It will probably be an even match.
That's what I'm hoping to see.
By monitoring both of your fighting abilities and reflexes, I will be able to gain insight into potential evotar shortcomings or superiorities.
If the duel proves to be one-sided, that could have major ramifications for the future of evotars.
That sounds pretty serious.
Gyahahaha! Afraid that I'm going to wipe the floor with you?
Oh not at all. I'm more worried for a normal player like yourself!
Excellent! I have a special PVP arena set up here in the lab.
You guys don't want to know how long it took to clear out the lab equipment for this space.
Please climb up and we can get started.
Ok, I am setting the victory condition to \c[3]10 points\c[0].
That should give me plenty of data.
Shizuka, could you turn on the fence?
Good luck, guys!
Let's do this!
You want to face me at \c[2]\v[tmp.fightLevel]\c[0]? Isn't handicapping me going to defeat the entire purpose of this experiment?
Uh, I'm sure Satoshi can adjust for it...
Level \c[1]\v[tmp.fightLevel]\c[0], huh? Seeking a challenge?
I'm not going easy on you!
Gyahahaha! Three in a row!
Your streak won't last much longer.
Wow, Lukas! You've won five in a row!
I know his every move.
I've won the last seven rounds. It seems like the results are clear.
You haven't won anything yet. This isn't over.
This is crazy! I have lost nine in a row!
This result is a little concerning.. I thought for sure that it would be an even match..
And the first round goes to humanity!
Oh we're just getting started.
Score one for Schneider!
Isn't that my name too?
How am I supposed to fight someone who knows all my moves?
Nice win, Lukas!
That was pretty tough. Hopefully I can keep this up.
I will certainly make sure you don't!
Well, I'm halfway there!
You've still got a long way to go!
What did you think of that?
I was going to do that exact move, you just got me first.
You got me again. I see you're putting my strategies to good use.
Your strategies? I've been doing that since before you existed!
Oh come on!
Almost there! Just one more to go!
What's the matter Lukas? I just won three in a row!
Oh it's just dumb luck.
Five in a row? So much for being equals.
Interesting. That is now seven in a row...
Glad I'm not the only one..
What is going on?! I've lost the last nine rounds in a row!
This is certainly not what I was expecting to see..
First round goes to team Evotar!
Beep. Boop. Your resistance is futile!
Nice try, I knew you were going to do that!
How are you able to predict my attacks so well?
How was that, Lea? I got him good!
Foolish human. You are dealing with superior intellect!
Oh brother...
I'm surprised that actually worked!
How am I supposed to beat you? You know exactly what I am going to do!
Well you're going to have to try a lot harder than that.
[applauds]
Another round for me!
That doesn't mean you are going to win the duel.
Looks like I am going to win!
What?! Luke?
Lukas?! What happened?

text.en_US: The rest of the mod is not yet implemented.

message.en_US: Uh, Lukas? I'm over here.

settings.name: Play sound\hud\quest-solved.ogg during the SHOW_BOARD_MSG that announces the teleporter unlocking at the end
Bonus music should only be allowed if Luke is 5 levels higher or Lv 99
Show "Booster" effect on Luke when duel starts if his level is higher than usual.

message.en_US: Hi!
Hello Lea. I'm busy helping my brother with something right now.
Perhaps another time.
Good luck, Lukas!
Just a word of advice, however. I've dueled Lea many times and this isn't going to be easy.
Oh don't worry. I'm not going easy on him!
Hi!
Hello there, Lea. What brings you to my lab?
Oh, I was calling you earlier because I was trying to find Luke and Lukas.
If you see them, please tell them to come visit me here.
I need their help with my work.
Hi!
Hello Lea. That was quite the duel, wasn't it?
[nods]
It's quite remarkable how well the human thought process is emulated by us Evotars.
Now if you'll excuse me, I still need to process all the data I collected.
When you're ready, please go join Luke on the arena.
Ready to go?
You bet I am!
Ok, Satoshi! Start it up!
I need a minute.
Hi Lea! You're going to be rooting for me, right?
Hey now! Are you picking favorites?
